ARTHRITIS, NEWBORNS - INDIA (DELHI) (03)
****************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Arthritis, newborns - India (Delhi) (02) 980318000106
Arthritis, newborns - India (Delhi): RFI 980306210312
Date: Sat, 13 Jun 1998 00:40:00 -0400 (EDT)
Forwarded by: Charu Prakash <cprakash@hsph.harvard.edu>

The first case of arthritis was detected on August 11, 1997 in a premature
child. Till March 30, 1998 a total of 21 cases of arthritis were recorded
among newborns. Most of the cases were preterm babies with birth weight of
less than 2.5 kg, except for three children.
